                                                        label.form-check-label(for="checkPolicy") I agreed to all policies, terms and conditions
                                                        .invalid-feedback You must agree before submitting.
                                                    .text-center
                                                        button.btn.btn-confirm(type="submit") Register
                                            .modal-footer
